data.description: This stunning Cape Coral single family home offers the perfect blend of luxury and functionality. With 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a 2 car garage, there's ample space for the whole family. The in-ground pool, complete with a pool heater, is perfect for year-round enjoyment. The Corian counters and stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen add a touch of elegance, while the tile flooring and new tile roof provide durability and style. The impacted doors and windows ensure safety and peace of mind. With Corian countertops in the bathrooms, formal dining area, and reverse osmosis throughout the home, this property truly has it all.
